beer.beer_description: A simple beer brewed with Jane the Queen tea blend from our dear friends at Tippity. Dreaming was brewed with German Pilsner malt. Flaked wheat, coriander seed, orange peel, Earl Grey tea and bergamot. This Belgian Wit has been can conditioned to preserve and enhance the flavours inside.
